headline.main: Jerry Sandusky Transferred to a Medium-Security Prison
headline.print_headline: Jerry Sandusky Transferred to a Medium-Security Prison

lead_paragraph: Former Penn State assistant football coach Jerry Sandusky has been moved from a maximum-security prison to a medium-security facility in western Pennsylvania.
